{"tid":568292,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 暑假莫斯科出發 去咩地方好?","createTime":"2018-02-21T15:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T03:54:02.000Z","uid":150930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0874d3f8d75c5941d558805007f451b1f2843408","tid":568292,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的, 黎緊7月第一站會去莫斯科一星期左右, 之後去第二度. 大約全程三星期番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前諗過去南美, 但依家睇睇啲機票已經加晒價, 重貴過係香港出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有諗過去中美, 好似古巴同墨西哥呢啲地方恥笑下何志平, 但個價又同香港出發差唔多.<br />\n之後見到去摩洛哥好似唔錯, 平過香港出發40%左右, 去到沙漠(雖然果時好熱), 重可以玩埋西葡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而去芬蘭都平, 但暑假冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全能既連登仔有冇咩特方推薦?<br />\n利申: 對歐洲古建築冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bbac4a0d94e8a3030e6479c7d51c66b6c6ea6e","tid":568292,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"七月撞正俄羅斯踢世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲要係正莫斯科踢，去邊都貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f6740a8eaefb9821b5c27dad21f298fa40e4d5","tid":568292,"uid":150930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63bbac4a0d94e8a3030e6479c7d51c66b6c6ea6e","tid":568292,"uid":71620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"七月撞正俄羅斯踢世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass